api_list.name: Jobs Classifier
api_list.description: Classify jobs based on education level, job function, seniority level using our state of the art AI model.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://job-search15.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "job-search15.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
